{
  "texts": [
    "Emotional categories included anger, anticipation, disgust, fear, joy, sadness, surprise and trust.",
    "We presented the data on conclusiveness as frequencies and percentages.",
    "Numerical data were checked for normality using the Shapiro-Wilk test and presented as medians with 95% confidence intervals.",
    "SMOG index was presented as a median with 95% CI.",
    "LIWC variables were described as scores from 0 to 100, which indicates the percentage of the words in a given text related to a specific LIWC category."
  ]
}